$500 in 1989-89 to $300 in 1990. Lower incentives are also offered
on the LeBaron Coupe Highline, Eagle Premier LX, Premier ES,
Premier LTD, and the New Yorker Landau with Mark Cross Edition
package.
   Chrysler said it would honor any higher cash allowance
previously available on vehicles delivered through Oct. 12.
   Cash back offers on other Dodge cars and trucks and Jeep models
remain the same as those for 1988-89 models.
